<h2>What's New</h2>

<h3>Added</h3>
<ul>
<li>Countdown timer in menu bar when usage reaches 100%</li>
<li>Reset notifications when usage window resets after being near/at limit</li>
<li>Keyboard shortcut tooltips on menu bar action buttons (Refresh, Settings, Quit)</li>
</ul>

<h3>Changed</h3>
<ul>
<li>Menu bar now shows time remaining until reset when at capacity</li>
</ul>

